tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: SELECT osVersion, count(*) from usersession WHERE usersession.applicationType = "MOBILE_APPLICATION" GROUP BY osVersion ORDER by count(*) DESC

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select count(*) as " " from usersession WHERE usersession.applicationType = "MOBILE_APPLICATION"

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select count(*) as " " from useraction WHERE usersession.applicationType = "MOBILE_APPLICATION"

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select AVG(duration) AS " " from useraction WHERE usersession.applicationType = "MOBILE_APPLICATION"

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select count(*) as " "  from useraction where requestErrorCount  >=1  AND usersession.applicationType = "MOBILE_APPLICATION"

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: SELECT  COUNT(*) AS " " FROM usersession WHERE useraction.hasCrash = true AND usersession.applicationType = "MOBILE_APPLICATION"

tiles.name: Crash count (by os and app version)
tiles.customName: Crash count (by os and app version)

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: SELECT top (useraction.name, 5) AS "Name", application AS "Domaine", COUNT(*) AS "User action > 12 s"  FROM useraction where  visuallyCompleteTime > 12000  AND usersession.applicationType = "MOBILE_APPLICATION" GROUP BY useraction.name, application   ORDER BY  count(*) DESC

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: SELECT top (useraction.name, 5) AS "Name", application AS "Domaine", COUNT(*) AS "User action with error"  FROM useraction where  requestErrorCount  >= 1 AND usersession.applicationType = "MOBILE_APPLICATION" GROUP BY useraction.name, application ORDER BY  count(*) DESC
